{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"多情的访问","authors":["洛雨"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联代表团正式访问中国的农村——京西郊海淀等地……，工农各界以土产品、园蔬、瓜果等礼物，献给国际友人，西蒙诺夫和斯托雷脱夫讲过很多的话，十分恳挚的感情，把新月疎星下的座谈会衬托得更加和谐完美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——本报北京廿五日专电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国的狄光啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明澈的高空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡漾着庄稼的芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西风的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"御着收获季的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢笑的飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着北国的秋光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西蒙诺夫、杜伯洛维娜…的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友爱的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻快的鼓动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友爱的脚步啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏过新修的村路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过新修的木桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到广袤的田野里来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到朴实的农村里来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的友人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难已经过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福已经来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可以自由的走来走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像走在你们自己的国土上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一寸土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也都是从斗争中得来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一粒黑土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也都充满着革命党人的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和善良人民的泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一次斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也为了祖国的解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一滴血泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也浸透着马列的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也割断了奴隶的枷锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的锄头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也挖去了封建的残根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的气流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也带着俄罗斯的寒汽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的居民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有着俄罗斯的果敢和坚强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也跟苏维埃的泥土一样肥沃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也跟苏维埃的乡村一样美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的友人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的思想相通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗帜相同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会懂得不同的言语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着国际友爱的光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的友人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们手和手紧握"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们的心灵和心灵拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要告诉你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的斗争的经验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也告诉我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们更丰富的战斗的史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要告诉你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们获得解放的欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也告诉我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的建设高潮的浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多谢你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的友人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们留下了多情的爱抚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了集体农场的远景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这新月一弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疏星灿烂的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也献给你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放的鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地上茁生的园蔬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里长大的瓜果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的记着我们啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也永远的记着你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记着你们的多情的访问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿七日晨"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}